.span-14.append-1
  :markdown
    TorqueBox is a new kind of Ruby application platform that integrates popular 
    technologies such as Ruby-on-Rails, while extending the footprint of Ruby 
    applications to include support for Job Scheduling, Task Queues, SOAP Handling, 
    and Telephony.
  
    TorqueBox provides an all-in-one environment, built upon the latest, most 
    powerful JBoss AS Java application server. Functionality such as clustering and 
    cloud deployment is included right out-of-the-box. 
  
